OL,3,CEx-footballer Joey Barton appears in
OL,4,Ccourt with assault charges
OL,6,FFormer footballer Joey Barton has been
OL,7,Fremanded in custody after appearing in
OL,8,Fcourt charged with an assault near a
OL,9,Fgolf club.
OL,11,FBarton, 43, from Widnes, Cheshire, is
OL,12,Faccused of assault occasioning
OL,13,Fgrievous bodily harm along with a
OL,14,Fsecond man, Gary O'Grady, 50, from
OL,15,FHuyton, Merseyside.
OL,17,FThey appeared at Liverpool Magistrates
OL,18,FCourt on Tuesday 10 March, accused of
OL,19,Fattacking Kevin Lynch at Fairway,
OL,20,FHuyton, on Sunday 8 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
