OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773234702
OL,3,CEx-footballer Joey Barton appears in
OL,4,Ccourt with assault charges
OL,6,FDistrict Judge James Hatton told
OL,7,FBarton he would be remanded in custody
OL,8,Funtil the hearing, while O'Grady was
OL,9,Freleased on conditional bail.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called at
OL,12,Faround 9pm on Sunday 8 March after a
OL,13,Fman suffered serious injuries to his
OL,14,Fface and body near Huyton and Prescot
OL,15,FGolf Club.
OL,17,FMerseyside Police said he is in a
OL,18,Fserious but stable condition in
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
