CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773234702
OL,3,CEx-footballer Joey Barton appears in
OL,4,Ccourt with assault charges
OL,6,FThe two defendants and the victim all
OL,7,Fappear on England Golf lists as
OL,8,Fmembers of the Huyton and Prescot Golf
OL,9,FClub.
OL,11,FJoey Barton made 269 appearances in
OL,12,Fthe Premier League, including 130 for
OL,13,FManchester City
OL,15,FFollowing his playing career he
OL,16,Fmanaged Fleetwood Town and Bristol
OL,17,FRovers.
OL,19,FThe men will appear at Liverpool Crown
OL,20,FCourt for a plea hearing on April 7.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
